                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">How do I get @@Nadeko to join my server?</h4>
                </div>
                <div id="module-1" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>Send her a Direct Message with -h to get the link. Only Server Owners can allow the bot to join.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel panel-default collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#module-2">
                <div class="faq-expand">
                    <i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus"></i>
                    <i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">I want to change permissions, but it doesn't work D:</h4>
                </div>
                <div id="module-2" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>To change permissions, you have to set the ;permsrole (default permission role is called <code>Nadeko</code>, you can create a role named like that and assign it to yourself).<i>Only the owner of the server can change permissions without having this role.</i></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
