                    <i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">Music doesn't work on a Mac?!</h4>
                </div>
                <div id="module-3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <p>You have to build <code>mono</code> from source. <a href="http://www.mono-project.com/docs/compiling-mono/mac/">http://www.mono-project.com/docs/compiling-mono/mac/</a>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
